Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.data.base.api.connection.data

Class DBConnection

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.data.base.api.connection.data.DBConnection
  • public final class DBConnection
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is designed to wrap data of a DB connection and and create the opened connection. Connection data is described by PersistenceUnitMetaData The resulted connection is represented by JDOPersistenceManagerFactory
